        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Directs the Secretary of Transportation (DOT) to carry out a pilot program to study the benefits of using hair specimens to conduct preemployment controlled substances tests of commercial motor vehicle operators.</p> <p>Directs the Secretary to develop guidelines, protocols, and standards for such tests.</p>]]></text>
